2016-10-31 07:30:15,594 [-] [PassThroughMessageProcessor-4]  INFO LogMediator To: /, MessageID: urn:uuid:390b0637-c52b-4dac-822d-ce478a7a92a1, Direction: request, AA = &amp;lt;a&amp;gt;&amp;lt;b/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;b/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;b/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;b/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Fix would be to clone the valueElement at the PropertyMediatorFactory&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead of &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (value != &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;) {
            propMediator.setValue(value.getAttributeValue(), dataType);
        } &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (valueElement != &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;) {
            propMediator.setValueElement(valueElement);


&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;p&gt;we need to use&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (value != &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;) {
            propMediator.setValue(value.getAttributeValue(), dataType);
        } &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (valueElement != &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;) {
            propMediator.setValueElement(valueElement.cloneOMElement());

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

